  "name": "Víctor Iván Sosa",
  "body_es": "<div class=\"section-featured is-featured-image\">\n\t<div class=\"featured-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_2194edit-1.jpg)\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"featured-wrap flex\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"featured-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"tags-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/artesanos/\">Artesanos</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/ceramica/\">Cerámica</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"post-tag global-tag\" href=\"/tag/estampa-tipica/\">Estampa Típica</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"white\">Víctor Iván Sosa, casitas típicas en barro</h1>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-meta white\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>El folklore puertorriqueño en tus manos</span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\t<div class=\"section-post wrap\">\n\t\t<div class=\"post-wrap \">\n\t\t\t<h3 id=\"documental-27\">Documental #27</h3><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2319edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_2319edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2025/01/DSC_2319edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2025/01/DSC_2319edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2025/01/DSC_2319edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Desde Carolina, Puerto Rico, el maestro artesano Víctor Iván Sosa lleva más de 48 años trabajando el barro, transformándolo en piezas llenas de identidad y memoria cultural. Reconocido por sus casitas típicas puertorriqueñas, su obra evoca la vida del campo, los recuerdos familiares y el legado de nuestros abuelos. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-card-hascaption\"><figcaption><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Duración: 8 minutos 🎬 | Recomendamos ver nuestros documentales con el teléfono en posición horizontal o, mejor aún, en familia desde tu \"smart TV\". Para esto último, búscanos como </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Obras del País</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> en el app de YouTube y </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">suscríbete</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 📺. Asegúrate de que la </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">calidad del video esté en 1080p ⚙️.</strong></b></p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-toggle-card\" data-kg-toggle-state=\"close\">\n            <div class=\"kg-toggle-heading\">\n                <h4 class=\"kg-toggle-heading-text\"><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Aviso de derechos de autor</strong></b></h4>\n                <button class=\"kg-toggle-card-icon\" aria-label=\"Expand toggle to read content\">\n                    <svg id=\"Regular\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                        <path class=\"cls-1\" d=\"M23.25,7.311,12.53,18.03a.749.749,0,0,1-1.06,0L.75,7.311\"></path>\n                    </svg>\n                </button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"kg-toggle-content\"><p><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Todo el contenido publicado por </span><i><em class=\"italic\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Obras del País</em></i><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> —incluyendo videos, audios, imágenes, textos y materiales gráficos— está protegido por derechos de autor.</span></p><p><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Agradecemos y fomentamos que compartas nuestro contenido utilizando los enlaces oficiales de nuestra página web y redes sociales.</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Eso nos ayuda a seguir difundiendo las historias que documentamos con tanto esmero.</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sin embargo, </span><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">no está permitido descargar, copiar, modificar ni volver a publicar nuestro contenido en otras plataformas sin autorización previa y sin el debido crédito.</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> El uso no autorizado afecta directamente el trabajo que realizamos junto a comunidades y artesanos en todo Puerto Rico.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Para más información sobre el uso adecuado de nuestro material, acceda </span><a href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/preguntas-frecuentes/\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">aquí</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Si deseas colaborar o compartir de otra manera, </span><a href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/contactanos/\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">contáctanos</span></a><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Estamos abiertos a alianzas que respeten y amplifiquen esta labor.</span></p></div>\n        </div><h2 id=\"informaci%C3%B3n-de-contacto-del-artesano\">Información de contacto del artesano:<br></h2><h3 id=\"victor-ivan-sosa\">Victor Ivan Sosa</h3><p>📍 Carolina<br>📞 787-347-8668<br>📧 quijote7636@yahoo.com<br>🌅 <strong>Instagram:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/victor_ivan_sosa/?hl=en&ref=obrasdelpais.com\" rel=\"noreferrer\">victor_ivan_sosa</a><br>👥 <strong>Facebook:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/estudio.arcilla\">Victor Iván Sosa</a><br><br>💲 Tiene piezas comenzando desde $20 hasta piezas de más de $150. Todo depende del tamaño y la complejidad de la pieza.</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-file-card\"><a class=\"kg-file-card-container\" href=\"https://www.obrasdelpais.com/content/files/2023/08/Victor-Ivan-Sosa.png\" title=\"Download\" download=\"\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-contents\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-title\">Victor Ivan Sosa - Casitas Típicas en Barro</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-caption\">Descarga el QR Code de este perfil.</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-metadata\"><div class=\"kg-file-card-filename\">Victor Ivan Sosa.png</div><div class=\"kg-file-card-filesize\">6 KB</div></div></div><div class=\"kg-file-card-icon\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><defs><style>.a{fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5px;}</style></defs><title>download-circle</title><polyline class=\"a\" points=\"8.25 14.25 12 18 15.75 14.25\"></polyline><line class=\"a\" x1=\"12\" y1=\"6.75\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"18\"></line><circle class=\"a\" cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11.25\"></circle></svg></div></a></div><p><strong>NOTA:</strong> <em>Obras del País no está vendiendo artesanías. Para conseguir piezas o coordinar talleres, comuníquese directamente con el artesano. </em>Cuando busques una pieza de colección o algo que regalar en un día especial, ¡piensa en un artesano boricua! ¡<em><strong>Y no olvides decirle que le conociste a través de Obras del País! </strong>🤗</em></p><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-yellow\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">✉️</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\"><b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">¡No te pierdas nuestras publicaciones!</strong></b><br>Suscríbete y entérate de nuevos estrenos, de lo que pasa en la comunidad artesanal y acompáñanos en este camino hacia documentar a 100 artesanos boricuas.</div></div><h2 id=\"\"></h2><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2237edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_2237edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2237edit.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2281edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_2281edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2281edit.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2291_01edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_2291_01edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2291_01edit.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"%C2%BFc%C3%B3mo-se-hace-una-casita-en-barro\">¿Cómo se hace una casita en barro? </h2><p>El artesano Víctor Iván Sosa nos muestra:</p><ol><li>Corta un pedazo de barro y lo aplasta en una tela canvas con dos planchitas a los lados para que quede al mismo nivel.</li></ol><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.04.29.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1126\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.04.29.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.04.29.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.04.29.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.04.29.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.06.49.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1117\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.06.49.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.06.49.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.06.49.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.06.49.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>2.   Corta las distintas partes de la casita, les hace los diseños y crea las ventanas y puertas.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.07.34.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1117\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.07.34.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.07.34.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.07.34.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.07.34.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>3.   Une las paredes con una mezcla barro, agua y vinagre.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.13.24.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1118\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.13.24.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.13.24.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.13.24.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.13.24.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_1068.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_1068.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_1068.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_1068.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_1068.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>4.   Una vez montada la casita, añade las incrustaciones de los clavos.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0001-1.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3108\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0001-1.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0001-1.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0001-1.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0001-1.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0009.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0009.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0009.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0009.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0009.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_1072.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_1072.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_1072.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_1072.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_1072.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>5.   Añade los zancos y el techo.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.14.23.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1354\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.14.23.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.14.23.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.14.23.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.14.23.png 2377w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0016-1.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0016-1.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0016-1.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0016-1.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0016-1.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0032.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0032.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0032.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0032.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0032.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>6.   Una vez ensambla el techo, entonces tiene que dejar secar la pieza. A veces toma de 3 a 5 días.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0041-2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2667\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0041-2.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0041-2.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0041-2.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0041-2.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>7.   Hornea la pieza.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.16.05.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1273\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.16.05.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.16.05.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.16.05.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.16.05.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0029.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0029.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0029.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0029.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0029.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>8.   Pinta la pieza y añade los detalles finales </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.17.54.png\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1369\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.17.54.png 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.17.54.png 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.17.54.png 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/Screen-Shot-2022-11-28-at-18.17.54.png 2351w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0019.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0019.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0019.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0019.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_0019.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>Pura magia <strong>✨</strong></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0041-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_0041-1.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_0041-1.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_0041-1.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_0041-1.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"%C2%A1gracias\">¡Gracias!</h3><p>¡Mil gracias a <strong>Víctor Iván Sosa</strong> por abrirnos las puertas a su taller! Y gracias a ustedes por leernos, por acompañarnos y por apoyar a los artesanos de Puerto Rico. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide kg-card-hascaption\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/IMG_0355.jpeg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/IMG_0355.jpeg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/IMG_0355.jpeg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/IMG_0355.jpeg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/IMG_0355.jpeg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"></div></div></div><figcaption><p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tras las cámaras | Víctor Sosa, Anisabel, Isaak, Lourdes</span></p></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2211edit.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2025/01/DSC_2211edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2025/01/DSC_2211edit.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h2 id=\"hay-historias-que-si-no-las-contamos-se-perder%C3%A1n-para-siempre\">Hay historias que, si no las contamos, se perderán para siempre...</h2><div class=\"kg-card kg-callout-card kg-callout-card-yellow\"><div class=\"kg-callout-emoji\">🤝</div><div class=\"kg-callout-text\">Obras del País es reconocida por el IRS como una entidad sin fines de lucro calificada bajo la Sección<b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> 501(c)(3)</strong></b>&nbsp;federal y&nbsp;<b><strong style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">1101.01 </strong></b>de PR. Esto significa que, a medida permitida por la ley, puedes restar tu donativo del ingreso bruto ajustado a la hora de presentar tu declaración de impuestos.<br><br>Los documentales van dirigidos a la preservación de nuestra herencia cultural y a la integración de la comunidad artesanal al mundo digital y educativo. Brindamos este servicio gratuitamente a los artesanos entrevistados. Tu donación permite la continuidad del proceso de coordinación, grabación, edición y publicidad de estos documentales, así como el acceso público a un archivo audiovisual del patrimonio artesanal de Puerto Rico.</div></div><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-gallery-card kg-width-wide\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-container\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-row\"><div class=\"kg-gallery-image\"><img src=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/2022/11/DSC_2307edit.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w600/2022/11/DSC_2307edit.jpg 600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1000/2022/11/DSC_2307edit.jpg 1000w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w1600/2022/11/DSC_2307edit.jpg 1600w, https://storage.ghost.io/c/0b/21/0b211f14-b12e-4e21-b608-435a1df6692c/content/images/size/w2400/2022/11/DSC_2307edit.jpg 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"></div></div></div></figure><p>¿Te quedaste con ganas de más? Síguenos en <strong>Instagram</strong> (<a href=\"https://instagram.com/obrasdelpais?utm_medium=copy_link&ref=obrasdelpais.com\">@obrasdelpais</a>) y <strong>Facebook</strong> (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/obrasdelpais/\">Obras del País</a>) para contenido adicional de cada artesano. Y si te gustó el corto documental, coméntalo y compártelo. Queremos saber qué opinan. 🤗✨</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div>\n</div>\t\t<div class=\"post-meta\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"post-share\">\r\n\t<a class=\"twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=V%C3%ADctor%20Iv%C3%A1n%20Sosa%2C%20casitas%20t%C3%ADpicas%20en%20barro&amp;url=https://www.obrasdelpais.com/victor-ivan-sosa-casitas-tipicas-en-barro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><svg class=\"global-svg\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M23.954 4.569c-.885.389-1.83.654-2.825.775 1.014-.611 1.794-1.574 2.163-2.723-.951.555-2.005.959-3.127 1.184-.896-.959-2.173-1.559-3.591-1.559-2.717 0-4.92 2.203-4.92 4.917 0 .39.045.765.127 1.124C7.691 8.094 4.066 6.13 1.64 3.161c-.427.722-.666 1.561-.666 2.475 0 1.71.87 3.213 2.188 4.096-.807-.026-1.566-.248-2.228-.616v.061c0 2.385 1.693 4.374 3.946 4.827-.413.111-.849.171-1.296.171-.314 0-.615-.03-.916-.086.631 1.953 2.445 3.377 4.604 3.417-1.68 1.319-3.809 2.105-6.102 2.105-.39 0-.779-.023-1.17-.067 2.189 1.394 